      "seq_in_scene": 26,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "倪厚"
      ],
      "text": "仁兄转来，仁兄转来。吓，想是走远了。",
      "text_length": 18
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01012006_e00027",
      "play_id": "01012006",
      "scene_id": "01012006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 27,
      "seq_in_scene": 27,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "殷碧莲"
      ],
      "text": "解元爷请来见礼。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01012006_e00028",
      "play_id": "01012006",
      "scene_id": "01012006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 28,
      "seq_in_scene": 28,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "倪厚"
      ],
      "text": "小娘子讲些什么？",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01012006_e00029",
      "play_id": "01012006",
      "scene_id": "01012006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 29,
      "seq_in_scene": 29,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "殷碧莲"
      ],
      "text": "适才在大王面前，刀下救我不死。当面谢过！",
      "text_length": 20
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01012006_e00030",
      "play_id": "01012006",
      "scene_id": "01012006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 30,
      "seq_in_scene": 30,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "倪厚"
      ],
      "text": "些须小事，何劳一谢。请坐。",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01012006_e00031",
      "play_id": "01012006",
      "scene_id": "01012006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 31,
      "seq_in_scene": 31,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "殷碧莲"
      ],
      "text": "有坐。请问解元爷，家住哪里？姓甚名谁？因何到此，与大王同伙？",
      "text_length": 30
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01012006_e00032",
      "play_id": "01012006",
      "scene_id": "01012006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 32,
      "seq_in_scene": 32,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "倪厚"
      ],
      "text": "生姓倪名厚，表字顺田，新驿县人氏。此山大王，乃是我的好友，请我饮宴，并无别事。",
      "text_length": 39
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01012006_e00033",
      "play_id": "01012006",
      "scene_id": "01012006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 33,
      "seq_in_scene": 33,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "殷碧莲"
      ],
      "text": "这就是了。请问解元爷，家中还有什么人？",
      "text_length": 19
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01012006_e00034",
      "play_id": "01012006",
      "scene_id": "01012006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 34,
      "seq_in_scene": 34,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "倪厚"
      ],
      "text": "小娘子既问，听生一言：",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01012006_e00035",
      "play_id": "01012006",
      "scene_id": "01012006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 35,
      "seq_in_scene": 35,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮慢板",
      "speakers": [
        "倪厚"
      ],
      "text": "有小生少年时父亡母寡，娶舍妻也算得贤良姣娃。住几间破草房房屋不大，家贫穷全靠着仿写字画。",
      "text_length": 44
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01012006_e00036",
      "play_id": "01012006",
      "scene_id": "01012006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 36,
      "seq_in_scene": 36,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "殷碧莲"
      ],
      "text": "听解元爷之言，家中还有婆婆、大娘子么？",
      "text_length": 19
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01012006_e00037",
      "play_id": "01012006",
      "scene_id": "01012006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 37,
      "seq_in_scene": 37,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "倪厚"
      ],
      "text": "啊？适才大王面前，救你不死，你倒当起真来了？",
      "text_length": 22
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01012006_e00038",
      "play_id": "01012006",
      "scene_id": "01012006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 38,
      "seq_in_scene": 38,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "殷碧莲"
      ],
      "text": "吓，解元爷，在大王面前拜罢天地，入了洞房，这婚姻之事，何以为假？",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01012006_e00039",
      "play_id": "01012006",
      "scene_id": "01012006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 39,
      "seq_in_scene": 39,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮慢板",
      "speakers": [
        "殷碧莲"
      ],
      "text": "拜天地入洞房何言为假？尊一声解元爷细听根芽：你救我不死那钢刀之下，像这样大人情怎样报答？",
      "text_length": 44
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01012006_e00040",
      "play_id": "01012006",
      "scene_id": "01012006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 40,
      "seq_in_scene": 40,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮原板",
      "speakers": [
        "倪厚"
      ],
      "text": "适才间我救你钢刀之下，不过是恻隐心暂且允答。你本是贵人妻必真不假，说这些不中听惹人笑话。",
      "text_length": 44
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01012006_e00041",
      "play_id": "01012006",
      "scene_id": "01012006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 41,
      "seq_in_scene": 41,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "殷碧莲"
      ],
      "text": "如此说来，奴多口了。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01012006_e00042",
      "play_id": "01012006",
      "scene_id": "01012006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 42,
      "seq_in_scene": 42,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "倪厚"
      ],
      "text": "你忒以地多口吓！",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01012006_e00043",
      "play_id": "01012006",
      "scene_id": "01012006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 43,
      "seq_in_scene": 43,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "殷碧莲"
      ],
      "text": "解元爷请过来拜揖！",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01012006_e00044",
      "play_id": "01012006",
      "scene_id": "01012006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 44,
      "seq_in_scene": 44,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "倪厚"
      ],
      "text": "小娘子有何话讲？",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01012006_e00045",
      "play_id": "01012006",
      "scene_id": "01012006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 45,
      "seq_in_scene": 45,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "殷碧莲"
      ],
      "text": "你看天夜深了，你我上床安眠。",
      "text_length": 14
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01012006_e00046",
      "play_id": "01012006",
      "scene_id": "01012006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 46,
      "seq_in_scene": 46,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "倪厚"
      ],
      "text": "小娘子请上床安眠，我在此地，一旁烤火。",
      "text_length": 19
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01012006_e00047",
      "play_id": "01012006",
      "scene_id": "01012006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 47,
      "seq_in_scene": 47,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "殷碧莲"
      ],
      "text": "如此，不恭了。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01012006_e00048",
      "play_id": "01012006",
      "scene_id": "01012006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 48,
      "seq_in_scene": 48,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "倪厚"
      ],
      "text": "礼该。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01012006_e00049",
      "play_id": "01012006",
      "scene_id": "01012006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 49,
      "seq_in_scene": 49,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "殷碧莲"
      ],
      "text": "占先了。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01012006_e00050",
      "play_id": "01012006",
      "scene_id": "01012006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 50,
      "seq_in_scene": 50,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "倪厚"
      ],
      "text": "岂敢。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01012006_e00051",
      "play_id": "01012006",
      "scene_id": "01012006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 51,
      "seq_in_scene": 51,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "殷碧莲"
      ],
      "text": "得罪了。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01012006_e00052",
      "play_id": "01012006",
      "scene_id": "01012006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 52,
      "seq_in_scene": 52,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "倪厚"
      ],
      "text": "岂敢岂敢哪。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01012006_e00053",
      "play_id": "01012006",
      "scene_id": "01012006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 53,
      "seq_in_scene": 53,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮慢板",
      "speakers": [
        "殷碧莲"
      ],
      "text": "解元爷只生得十分好看，他好比小潘郎俱是一般。我只得上床去罗帐高悬，今夜晚但看他怎样终场？",
      "text_length": 44
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01012006_e00054",
      "play_id": "01012006",
      "scene_id": "01012006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 54,
      "seq_in_scene": 54,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "倪厚"
      ],
      "text": "哎，妙吓！小娘子睡在床上，如同酒醉海棠一般，叫我年少之人，如何忍耐得住？吓，不免上床与她安眠了罢。慢、慢、慢、慢着！",
      "text_length": 58
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01012006_e00055",
      "play_id": "01012006",
      "scene_id": "01012006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 55,
      "seq_in_scene": 55,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮原板",
      "speakers": [
        "倪厚"
      ],
      "text": "想起了我的娘吩咐之话：她叫我中途路少要贪花。我本是鱼得水还未变化，此一去跳龙门舞爪伸牙。",
      "text_length": 44
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01012006_e00056",
      "play_id": "01012006",
      "scene_id": "01012006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 56,
      "seq_in_scene": 56,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "殷碧莲"
      ],
      "text": "好困吓。看天到这般时候，他还在那里烤火。不免下床与他明讲了罢。吓，解元爷，上床安眠。",
      "text_length": 42
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01012006_e00057",
      "play_id": "01012006",
      "scene_id": "01012006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 57,
      "seq_in_scene": 57,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "倪厚"
      ],
      "text": "还是下面奉陪。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01012006_e00058",
      "play_id": "01012006",
      "scene_id": "01012006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 58,
      "seq_in_scene": 58,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "殷碧莲"
      ],
      "text": "解元爷请安眠。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01012006_e00059",
      "play_id": "01012006",
      "scene_id": "01012006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 59,
      "seq_in_scene": 59,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "倪厚"
      ],
      "text": "你请上床安眠。我在此地奉陪。",
      "text_length": 14
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01012006_e00060",
      "play_id": "01012006",
      "scene_id": "01012006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 60,
      "seq_in_scene": 60,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "殷碧莲"
      ],
      "text": "解元爷，奴有下言告禀。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01012006_e00061",
      "play_id": "01012006",
      "scene_id": "01012006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 61,
      "seq_in_scene": 61,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "倪厚"
      ],
      "text": "小娘子有话，落坐请讲。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01012006_e00062",
      "play_id": "01012006",
      "scene_id": "01012006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 62,
      "seq_in_scene": 62,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "殷碧莲"
      ],
      "text": "奴家姓殷，小字碧莲。我父官居一品，自幼将奴许配张郎为妻。是奴见他生得丑陋，无心于他。因此我主仆连夜逃出潼关。路过此山，被大王抢上山来。蒙解元爷救我不死，当着大王拜罢天地，入了洞房。这婚姻之事，托付你身上了。",
      "text_length": 103
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01012006_e00063",
      "play_id": "01012006",
      "scene_id": "01012006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 63,
      "seq_in_scene": 63,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮慢板",
      "speakers": [
        "殷碧莲"
      ],
      "text": "与解元对坐在洞房之下，你听我把此话细说根芽：我本是闺门女必真不假，为什么今夜晚不睬奴家？",
      "text_length": 44
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01012006_e00064",
      "play_id": "01012006",
      "scene_id": "01012006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 64,
      "seq_in_scene": 64,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮原板",
      "speakers": [
        "倪厚"
      ],
      "text": "今夜晚非是我装聋卖哑，都只为少华山男女混杂。但愿得咱二人同把山下，你往东我往西各奔天涯。",
      "text_length": 44
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01012006_e00065",
      "play_id": "01012006",
      "scene_id": "01012006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 65,
      "seq_in_scene": 65,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮原板",
      "speakers": [
        "殷碧莲"
      ],
      "text": "解元爷讲的是离别之话，倒叫我一阵阵意软心麻。到明天我二人同把山下，下山去咱二人再作计法。",
      "text_length": 44
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01012006_e00066",
      "play_id": "01012006",
      "scene_id": "01012006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 66,
      "seq_in_scene": 66,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "大王上，四龙套同上。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01012006_e00067",
      "play_id": "01012006",
      "scene_id": "01012006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 67,
      "seq_in_scene": 67,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "大王"
      ],
      "text": "仁兄起床来了？",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01012006_e00068",
      "play_id": "01012006",
      "scene_id": "01012006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 68,
      "seq_in_scene": 68,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "倪厚"
      ],
      "text": "起床来了。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01012006_e00069",
      "play_id": "01012006",
      "scene_id": "01012006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 69,
      "seq_in_scene": 69,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "大王"
      ],
      "text": "为何起得这等甚早？",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01012006_e00070",
      "play_id": "01012006",
      "scene_id": "01012006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 70,
      "seq_in_scene": 70,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
